{"type":"after","callId":"call@90","endTime":167902.917,"result":{"value":"\nOPERATIONS\nMCPD Portal\nDashboard\nNavigator\nForms\nSaved Work\nReports\nAuthority\nOperations\nPersonnel\nAdmin\nSIGNED IN AS\nrobertrichards\nWebsite Controller\n127.0.0.1:8092\nRole: Website Controller\nScope\nLogout\nDESKTOP INCIDENT INTAKE\nStart a report from the same scenarios officers use on mobile.\nSelect a call type to seed the report shell. The mobile scenario builder controls what appears here.\nManage Scenarios\n1. Choose scenario\n\nDOMESTIC\nDomestic Disturbance\nPrimary domestic response, scene control, initial statements, and follow-up paperwork prep.\n\nSUSPICIOUS\nSuspicious Person\nField contact and articulable-facts workflow for suspicious behavior and security concerns.\n\nTHEFT\nTheft\nProperty crime workflow focused on ownership, recovered items, and evidence trail.\n\nTRAFFIC\nTraffic Accident\nCollision response, roadway safety, vehicle data capture, and tow/impound preparation.\n\nTRESPASS\nTrespass After Warning\nReturn-after-warning workflow with authority review and citation/notice support.\n2. Name the report\nReport title\n\nChoose a scenario or type a report title to begin.\nCancel\nCreate Report"},"afterSnapshot":"after@call@90"}
