{"type":"after","callId":"call@126","endTime":177974.539,"result":{"value":"\nOPERATIONS\nMCPD Portal\nDashboard\nNavigator\nForms\nSaved Work\nReports\nAuthority\nOperations\nPersonnel\nAdmin\nSIGNED IN AS\nrobertrichards\nWebsite Controller\n127.0.0.1:8092\nRole: Website Controller\nScope\nLogout\nORDERS DESK\nSearch approved USMC orders and memorandums without the junk.\nResults stay inside the controlled library. Search by duty, workflow, standard, or operational phrase, then open the official source text that best fits the problem in front of you.\nSEARCH SCOPE\nApproved library only\nBEST INPUT\nDuties, procedures, standards, watch tasks\nAdmin Order Tools\nSearch\n\nSearch\nReset\nFilters\nStatus:\nActive only\nSEARCH BRIEF\nOpen Evidence Collection, Packaging, and Chain of Custody first. It ranked highest based on No search phrase applied.\nBEST MATCH TO OPEN FIRST\nEvidence Collection, Packaging, and Chain of Custody\nEvidence handling and chain-of-custody requirements from field collection to property room intake.\nMCLB_ALBANY_ORDER\n52%\nOperational Excerpt\nEvidence handling and chain-of-custody requirements from field collection to property room intake.\nWhy It Rose To The Top\nNo search phrase applied\nOpen Full Text\nDownload not available\nAdditional Results\n29 matches from approved sources.\nInstallation Access Control and Gate Search Authority\nMCLB_ALBANY_ORDER\nActive\nTraffic Stop and Enforcement Procedures\nMCLB_ALBANY_ORDER\nActive\nDesk Sergeant Shift Responsibilities\nMEMORANDUM\nDesk Sergeants\nActive\nGovernment Vehicle Use and Dispatch Policy\nMCLB_ALBANY_ORDER\nMarines\nActive\nCivilian Employee Timekeeping and Overtime Guidance\nMEMORANDUM\nCivilian Employees\nActive\nHarassment, Threat Communications, and Protective Actions\nMEMORANDUM\nActive\nShoplifting and Exchange/PX Theft Response Procedure\nMCLB_ALBANY_ORDER\nActive\nEvidence Photo and Digital Media Management\nMEMORANDUM\nActive\nPost Orders and Patrol Zone Responsibilities\nMCLB_ALBANY_ORDER\nActive\nDuty Officer Incident Brief and Sitrep Format\nMEMORANDUM\nActive\nSuspicious Package and Bomb Threat Response\nMEMORANDUM\nActive\nJuvenile Incident and Referral Procedures\nMCLB_ALBANY_ORDER\nActive\nImpaired Driving Enforcement and Field Sobriety Procedures\nMEMORANDUM\nActive\nVehicle Registration and Insurance Compliance on Base\nMCLB_ALBANY_ORDER\nActive\nBarracks Disturbance and Disorderly Conduct Enforcement\nMCLB_ALBANY_ORDER\nActive\nWatch Commander Duty and Notification Matrix\nMEMORANDUM\nActive\nLost or Stolen CAC and Access Credential Response\nMEMORANDUM\nActive\nPhysical Training and Fitness Program Standards\nUSMC_ORDER\nMarines\nActive\nDuty Roster and Watch Bill Management\nMCLB_ALBANY_ORDER\nCommand\nActive\nTattoo and Body Art Policy\nUSMC_ORDER\nMarines\nActive\nSearch and Seizure Standards for Installation Law Enforcement\nUSMC_ORDER\nActive\nUse of Force Reporting and Supervisor Review\nUSMC_ORDER\nActive\nMilitary Protective Order and Civil Protective Order Coordination\nUSMC_ORDER\nActive\nDomestic Violence Incident Response Requirements\nUSMC_ORDER\nActive\nSaluting, Customs, and Military Courtesies\nUSMC_ORDER\nMarines\nActive\nLeave and Liberty Administrative Procedures\nUSMC_ORDER\nMarines\nActive\nMarine Corps Grooming and Haircut Standards\nUSMC_ORDER\nMarines\nActive\nWeapons Carry, Storage, and Armory Check-Out Controls\nUSMC_ORDER\nActive\n"},"afterSnapshot":"after@call@126"}
